It's always impossible to hide the comfort that the @cr7cristianoronaldo Underwear collection provides and the fun that we have every time we shoot a campaign. 
 
Especially behind the scenes. 😉 

#CR7UNDERWEAR

Proud to be partnering with @binance 🙏
 
Together we'll give you the opportunity to own an iconic piece of sports history.
 
I'm excited to take this journey with all of you. Let’s change the NFT game with #Binance.

I'm an Ambassador for upcoming football video game UFL, where my #CR7FansTeam will be present, and it is up to you to pick its lineup! Suggest your favorite players on UFL social media in 3 rounds between June 7 and June 28.

Simply follow the updates and comment your suggestions. See more details in @uflgame bio! 📝

Proud to be part of the Nike family and excited to celebrate their first 50 years. Throughout my entire career we have been on a journey together, a journey of progress. And we have achieved some amazing results. Think you’ve seen it all? Think again: we are never done!
@nike #teamnike #nike50

You need more than quick feet to be a champion. It takes hours of hard work, stubborn determination and a dose of fearlessness.
 #KeepAClearHead #beclearbefearless #bethefirstyou #clearxcr7

We’re opening a new Insparya clinic in Valencia! The 3rd in Spain and the 8th @insparya_es Group clinic.

The new clinic offers 1,600 m2, 12 premium hair transplant rooms, 4 treatment rooms and the most advanced technology in this area, developed by our R+D Insparya Science and Clinical Institute.

This new clinic is a major milestone for the group. Thank you to our amazing team and the 45,000 patients who trusted in @insparya_es .🙏🏽

#Valencia #NewOpening #ComingSoon #Insparya #ClinicaCapilar

Never let doubts or dandruff hold you back.

When the time comes, clear your head and unleash your fearless power.
#KeepAClearHead #BeClearBeFearless #BeTheFirstYou

Proud to overcome one more challenge by becoming the World’s Clubs Top Goal Scorer, only 6 months after becoming the World’s International Top Goal Scorer. Nothing but respect for Romário, one of the best strikers of all time! Thanks to all the players that I’ve come across throughout my career, thanks to all the clubs that I represented, thanks to all my fans, and above all, thanks to my wonderful family. I couldn’t have done it without you! 👏🏽🙏🏽

Seven years of my career were played in the Premier League, making this my 8th season living in England. Throughout these years, I’ve felt the everlasting love of the UK for it’s Queen, and how important Her Majesty was and will forever be to the British people. I pay my respect to her memory and I mourn this irreplaceable loss with the country that I’ve learned to call home. My thoughts and prayers are with the Royal Family. 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻
